    </definition>
    <definition id="fs-id1163713284371">
      <term class="no-emphasis" cmlnle:reference="hipoteza Plancka o kwantach energii">hipoteza Plancka o kwantach energii (ang. <foreign><term cxlxt:index="foreign" class="no-emphasis">Planck’s hypothesis of energy quanta</term></foreign>)</term>
